title: Brett Beukeboom
text:
Brett Gary Beukeboom (born 13 August 1990) is a former <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> lock who played for <a href="Canada%20national%20rugby%20union%20team">Canada</a>.
Beukeboom made his debut for Canada in 2012 and was part of the Canada squad at the <a href="2015%20Rugby%20World%20Cup">2015 Rugby World Cup</a>.
